welcome_message_body: "Welcome to charming Cowell, Australia! Known for its stunning coastal views and friendly community, we invite you to explore and experience all that this beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Cowell Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Cowell Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport. No password required.
